definition: "water" radical in Chinese characters (Kangxi radical 85), occurring in 没, 法, 流 etc/see also 三點水|三点水[san1 dian3 shui3]

sentences.english: Clean and bright, You look happy to meet me.

sentences.english: Chen Jie is on LiuYun's left.

sentences.english: And they shall teach my people the difference between holy and profane, and shew them how to discern between clean and unclean.
sentences.chinese: 他們應教訓我的百姓區別聖與俗，知道潔與不潔。

sentences.english: The next semester, Jessica tried again.
sentences.chinese: 在接下來的那個學期，潔西卡再次嘗試。

sentences.english: The teacher love classmate, the world be the great, the tallest Jie.
sentences.chinese: 老師對同學的愛，天下最偉大，最高潔。

sentences.english: It was about time that Jessica got rid of that no-good boyfriend!

sentences.english: Jessica, an old friend of mine, went to a concert over the weekend.
sentences.chinese: 我的老朋友潔西卡上週末去聽了一場演唱會。

sentences.english: Diglant SY - D001 with olive design, clean slips through the first luxury.

sentences.chinese: 陳潔嘗試爲歐力佛在北京做一名導遊。你能幫助她麼？

sentences.english: We are your friends Mark, along with Wen-Jie.
sentences.chinese: 我們是你的廣播朋友馬可和文潔。

sentences.english: Enjoy teeth-cleaning chews or biscuits and tooth brushing three times per week.
